red;\"><strong>善用回覆不推功能</strong></span>"},{"pid":"045fe517dba53329de13c015099e71298c726416","tid":1451521,"uid":34063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:27:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你老母！<br />\n邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你老母！<br />\n邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你老母！</span><br />\n<br />\n邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你哋老母！要嬴嘅全部同我入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBbvRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBbvRS</a><br />\n<br />\n推,所有掟磚同火魔法都係黑警扮示威者做既<br />\n緊記要事：<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas<br />\n5.一米同胡椒球對人發射<br />\n6.罔顧安全,推人落電梯<br />\n7.黑警插贓嫁禍,塞管狀物體入示威者背囊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POs3Lz7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOs3Lz7.jpg&h=6417b1c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5aa9537eb6c8a2b0c54e8ac5af0d4a55be56af1","tid":1451521,"uid":86246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:27:53.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐咁你有咩高見 選票要等到11月尾喎"},{"pid":"ba5e8ffac1c67e5c306282485ca3f436b0af5734","tid":1451521,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:27:56.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母啊"},{"pid":"5ecd295fabeb8ceb2eda4d2e7a9aeacbc42efc50","tid":1451521,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:28:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不推回覆please</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7ced3955cf929403448fe0e6529069d09e166412","tid":1451521,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:28:14.000Z","msg":"妄想用一個已經腐敗嘅議會制度去處理腐敗嘅政府，樓主真係神邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家嘅議會最多最多只係可以阻止到更加多惡法通過（前提係泛民過半數），並唔可以廢除已經通過嘅惡法（因為有功能組別）"},{"pid":"33eecfa878aab36c664877e63d628d43a27704ec","tid":1451521,"uid":152594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:28:20.000Z","msg":"選票有用就唔會搞到今日咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g